org.webcurator.core.notification
Interface InTrayResource

All Known Subinterfaces:
AgencyInTrayResource, UserInTrayResource
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTarget, ArcHarvestResult, HarvestResult, Permission, Target, TargetGroup, TargetInstance
public interface InTrayResource

Provides the appropriate information required by the InTrayManager to build automated hyperlinks to the resource in question. For example this interface should be implemented by any WCT object that a Task or Notification is refers to.
